               <p>I am a watchman; I took the prisoner soon after on information; he had a bundle of hay and brickdust under his arm, tied up like muslin; the direction is 
               <persName id="t17900113-64-person666">
                  John
                   Williams
               <interp inst="t17900113-64-person666" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
